1
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:26,750
[A Splendid Match]

2
00:01:27,490 --> 00:01:29,450
[Episode 28]

3
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,479
I heard that

4
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:35,840
Second Master Chen

5
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:38,229
specifically requested a leave of absence

6
00:01:38,229 --> 00:01:40,350
for your wedding with Third Master.

7
00:01:41,229 --> 00:01:42,229
He is rushing back

8
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:44,280
from Shaanxi now.

9
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:46,170
This also shows that

10
00:01:46,509 --> 00:01:48,710
Third Master really values

11
00:01:49,509 --> 00:01:51,150
this marriage.

12
00:01:51,950 --> 00:01:53,560
I can rest assured now.

13
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:55,120
Ms. Tong.

14
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:55,710
Yes.

15
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:57,229
Tell everyone to disperse.

16
00:01:57,229 --> 00:01:57,870
Yes.

17
00:01:58,870 --> 00:02:00,400
Come, follow me.

18
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,420
[Chen-Zhang] [Chen Yanzhang]

19
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:10,720
[Happiness]

20
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:18,800
[Chen Yanzhang] [Qin Xianlan]

21
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:20,050
[Chen Yanwen] [Wang]

22
00:02:20,180 --> 00:02:23,170
[Happiness]

23
00:02:34,140 --> 00:02:34,829
[Chen-Zhang]

24
00:02:34,850 --> 00:02:37,020
[Chen Yanzhang] [Chen Yanyun] [Chen Yanwen]
[Chen Yanpu] [Chen Xuanqing]

25
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,140
This old friend of mine

26
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:39,950
has been stubborn since she was little.

27
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:42,070
She can't stand opposition,

28
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:45,120
nor does she like ostentation from others.

29
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,600
I plan to be more restrained.

30
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,030
I will only say

31
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,610
nice things in front of her.

32
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,630
That's right.

33
00:02:55,910 --> 00:02:58,990
Third Master has two elder brothers.

34
00:02:59,079 --> 00:03:00,680
Both are born of concubines.

35
00:03:00,750 --> 00:03:01,590
Eldest Master

36
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,400
caught malaria

37
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:04,590
and passed away

38
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:05,800
at the age of twenty.

39
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:08,080
Second Master grew up

40
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:10,070
with Old Madam

41
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,470
and is highly valued.

42
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,240
Now,

43
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:16,910
he is the Provincial Administration
Commissioner in Shaanxi.

44
00:03:16,910 --> 00:03:19,000
His wife, Qin,

45
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:22,360
is from the Qin family in Zhending.

46
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,590
Because of her high birth,

47
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:28,600
she took charge of the household
as soon as she married in.

48
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:31,880
But because Second Master is posted away
all year round,

49
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:34,840
Qin has to run back and forth.

50
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:36,430
She may not

51
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:39,440
be able to manage the household
indefinitely.

52
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,680
I hope she could keep managing it.

53
00:03:45,310 --> 00:03:46,240
Why?

54
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,870
Don't you want to be

55
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:50,560
the madam in charge?

56
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:54,000
I used to think that if I didn't
manage the household,

57
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,730
I would definitely be bullied.

58
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:58,430
Now I understand.

59
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,800
Managing the household
takes a lot of effort,

60
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,750
and you don't get any thanks for it.

61
00:04:01,750 --> 00:04:02,710
and I even have to

62
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:04,440
subsidize it with my own money.

63
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:06,280
With this time and effort,

64
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,910
I'd be better off focusing on managing

65
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:08,970
my own properties.

66
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,260
Isn't this better than anything?

67
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,310
Well said.

68
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,240
As long as you know

69
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,120
not to fight over that little bit of power

70
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,240
in that mansion,

71
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,720
I haven't raised you in vain.

72
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:29,070
After Third Master is Fourth Master Chen.

73
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:31,270
He is Third Master's own young brother.

74
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,630
He also passed the provincial exam
earlier.

75
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,640
But later, for some reason,

76
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:40,270
he never took the metropolitan exam again.

77
00:04:40,490 --> 00:04:42,870
He just manages the chores in the mansion.

78
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:46,620
I heard Third Master mention it once.

79
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,240
It should be due to seizure disorder.

80
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,040
Third Master even told you

81
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,310
about this as well?

82
00:04:56,310 --> 00:04:57,630
Since Third Master

83
00:04:58,120 --> 00:05:00,390
has told you all these things,

84
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:03,620
I don't need to say more.

85
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:04,680
Presumably,

86
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,460
you know as much as I do.

87
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,190
No.

88
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:11,390
I want to hear it from you, Grandmother.

89
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:13,560
Don't you find me annoying?

90
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:15,600
Of course not.

91
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,360
When you say these things to me,

92
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:19,360
I still feel

93
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,600
like a child

94
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,880
fearless of everything.

95
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:24,800
If I do anything wrong,

96
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,480
you will always cover for me.

97
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,630
Silly child.

98
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,380
You are about to get married,

99
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:33,270
yet you still act so spoiled.

100
00:05:35,070 --> 00:05:36,000
Grandmother,

101
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:38,560
I can't bear to leave you.

102
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,270
I can't bear

103
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,560
to let you go either.

104
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:50,680
You are a blessed child.

105
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,220
In the future, with Third Master,

106
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:55,430
discuss everything

107
00:05:55,510 --> 00:05:57,170
and live a good life together.

108
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:11,190
[Gu Mansion]

109
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:12,440
It's raining.

110
00:06:12,470 --> 00:06:14,310
Everyone, be careful.

111
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,480
Don't bump or drop anything.

112
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:19,020
If anyone makes a mistake tomorrow,

113
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:20,640
I'll tan their hide!

114
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:21,800
-Yes!
-Yes!

115
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:26,200
[Gu]

116
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:29,460
Hya!

117
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:32,480
[Gu]

118
00:06:38,390 --> 00:06:39,250
Your Lordship,

119
00:06:39,450 --> 00:06:40,570
what brings you here?

120
00:06:40,570 --> 00:06:42,020
To add some dowry items
for your young lady.

121
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:44,150
[Gu Mansion]

122
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:43,480
This... this...

123
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,380
This...

124
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:50,240
Dezhu!

125
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,310
Baoning.

126
00:06:51,350 --> 00:06:52,480
Go to the Chen family to report the news.

127
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:52,880
Hurry!

128
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:16,130
[Fair Morning, Fine Hour]

129
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,070
Wait here.

130
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:29,950
Yes.

131
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:31,840
Young Lord Ye, please wait!

132
00:07:40,510 --> 00:07:41,909
Your eyes are so swollen.

133
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,400
You mustn't cry anymore.

134
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,190
Tomorrow, once the veil is on,

135
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:47,250
I won't see anyone.

136
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:48,560
My Lady.

137
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:51,370
Won't the Third Master lift your veil?

138
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,840
Young Lord Ye,

139
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,510
Zhao is getting married tomorrow.

140
00:07:58,510 --> 00:07:59,870
You are a man outside the family.

141
00:07:59,870 --> 00:08:01,160
Please consider

142
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:02,400
Zhao's reputation.

143
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,410
Reputation?

144
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,560
What's there to fear?

145
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:12,510
Am I not her uncle?

146
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:15,380
Young Lord Ye, please don't!

147
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,570
Li Xianhuai!

148
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,620
What's that sound?

149
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:31,480
Go,

150
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,900
get someone to bring a chair over.

151
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:36,390
But he is the Young Lord Ye.

152
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:39,130
Do you want to offend Chen Yanyun?

153
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,770
Hurry and go get a chair!

154
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:55,690
[Generations of Excellence]

155
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,550
My Lady,

156
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:02,800
it sounds like it's Young Lord Ye.

157
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:14,530
♪ Moonlight spills over the lapels of
my gown ♪

158
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:22,240
♪ My longing receives no reply ♪

159
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:29,280
♪ Wind rises, silently dissipating
from my heart ♪

160
00:09:32,530 --> 00:09:38,340
♪ That is the morning I missed ♪

161
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:44,160
♪ Ink stains spread on the letter paper ♪

162
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:47,840
Don't open it.

163
00:09:47,810 --> 00:09:51,530
♪ Outlining an unfinished poem ♪

164
00:09:51,660 --> 00:09:53,220
Are you feeling better?

165
00:09:53,690 --> 00:09:59,220
♪ Lamplight gently flickers
at the corners of my eyes ♪

166
00:10:01,710 --> 00:10:07,110
♪ Reflecting the empty memories ♪

167
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:11,500
♪ I gently murmur your name ♪

168
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:15,220
♪ Like snowflakes falling into the palm ♪

169
00:10:15,970 --> 00:10:18,610
♪ Before I can hold them up
for you to see clearly ♪

170
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,140
I still remember that time...

171
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:22,180
♪ They have already melted into teardrops
falling into my hands ♪

172
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:21,750
You came to my coming-of-age ceremony.

173
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,600
I went against my father

174
00:10:23,330 --> 00:10:26,230
♪ I gently write of parting ♪

175
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,510
in front of everyone.

176
00:10:26,950 --> 00:10:28,380
You were the first to step forward

177
00:10:27,130 --> 00:10:30,320
♪ Like fleeting fireflies
losing their trace ♪

178
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,150
and speak for me.

179
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:33,270
Three people can build
perfect harmony too.

180
00:10:31,310 --> 00:10:33,430
♪ Before I can inscribe the ending ♪

181
00:10:33,910 --> 00:10:34,550
Well said!

182
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:37,740
♪ It was already destined, in this life,
hard to promise each other ♪

183
00:10:35,270 --> 00:10:36,600
You should be rewarded.

184
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,750
From then on,

185
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:41,450
I owed you a debt of gratitude.

186
00:10:42,250 --> 00:10:45,060
♪ Worries have built a gate
within my heart ♪

187
00:10:43,620 --> 00:10:44,710
Later,

188
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,100
I took your carriage

189
00:10:46,230 --> 00:10:48,890
♪ Yet the oath will not succumb ♪

190
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,480
to Sili Hutong.

191
00:10:49,940 --> 00:10:51,960
♪ In dreams, I piece together
the lingering warmth ♪

192
00:10:50,910 --> 00:10:52,240
You also helped me

193
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,600
give my father

194
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:56,560
♪ Whose kiss does the deep love trap? ♪

195
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,730
a show of force,

196
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:57,830
helping me find my footing

197
00:10:57,310 --> 00:10:59,770
♪ The chessboard, black and white pieces
like stars ♪

198
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:59,460
in that unfamiliar home.

199
00:11:01,110 --> 00:11:03,610
♪ I play alone until dawn breaks ♪

200
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:05,150
Even later,

201
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,830
♪ This single move has trapped time ♪

202
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:09,340
you helped me many more times.

203
00:11:07,770 --> 00:11:10,390
♪ And trapped me as well ♪

204
00:11:11,550 --> 00:11:13,350
Don't talk about me helping you.

205
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:17,420
Let's just talk about you helping me.

206
00:11:20,410 --> 00:11:21,740
Before the palace coup,

207
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:25,080
you rushed back to the capital
from Tongzhou

208
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,220
to bring me news,

209
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,920
taking a huge personal risk.

210
00:11:29,870 --> 00:11:30,790
You were even willing to

211
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:31,990
risk your life for me.

212
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,630
Yet you say

213
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:39,430
you don't have even a little bit of
fondness for me?

214
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:40,630
That's different.

215
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,760
How is it different?

216
00:11:44,090 --> 00:11:45,550
Do you resent that I never

217
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:51,160
explicitly stated I wanted to marry you?

218
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:53,270
No.

219
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,360
Ye Xian.

220
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:02,360
I'm willing to

221
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,630
risk my life for you.

222
00:12:05,890 --> 00:12:07,190
But it's not only romantic love

223
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:09,190
that makes someone risk their life.

224
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,600
Friendship can too.

225
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,630
Friends.

226
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,590
Just friends?

227
00:12:42,340 --> 00:12:44,680
♪ The long night stretches
beyond the street ♪

228
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:48,190
♪ Longing piles up like snowdrifts ♪

229
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:51,810
♪ I gaze at the moon, praying
for a dream ♪

230
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,450
There is no umbrella in my room.

231
00:12:52,450 --> 00:12:53,190
It's cold outside.

232
00:12:52,620 --> 00:12:55,430
♪ In the dream, your footsteps are light ♪

233
00:12:53,330 --> 00:12:54,310
Put this on.

234
00:12:56,350 --> 00:12:59,300
♪ Softly, I gaze at that silhouette ♪

235
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:03,430
♪ Like the sunset sinking
behind distant ridges ♪

236
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:06,690
♪ Using all the strength of my
remaining years ♪

237
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:12,140
♪ I could not hold you back
to say goodbye ♪

238
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:15,660
You might

239
00:13:14,940 --> 00:13:17,920
♪ Gently, I sigh at that scene ♪

240
00:13:16,590 --> 00:13:17,960
not believe it.

241
00:13:18,950 --> 00:13:21,790
♪ Like a swing still in an empty
courtyard ♪

242
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,000
Actually,

243
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,080
since I was little,

244
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:26,370
♪ Before I can grasp the past tightly ♪

245
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:25,610
I haven't had many friends

246
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:27,750
apart from my family.

247
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:37,130
♪ Only memories remain, drifting lightly ♪

248
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:33,200
I could even say

249
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,370
that you are my only friend.

250
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,320
Others say

251
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:41,320
you have an eccentric and odd temper.

252
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,200
But I know

253
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:43,890
that it's not oddness.

254
00:13:45,550 --> 00:13:46,440
You just

255
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,870
don't know how to act.

256
00:13:53,270 --> 00:13:54,490
I'm the same.

257
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,750
I'm the eldest daughter,

258
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,840
but I've always

259
00:13:58,910 --> 00:14:00,570
had to be away from my parents.

260
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:04,600
No matter how well others treat me,

261
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:07,320
I still feel

262
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:11,120
like a piece of my heart
is forever missing.

263
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:14,990
As for being tricky and eccentric,

264
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:16,240
and arrogant,

265
00:14:17,790 --> 00:14:19,660
it's just because I was so scared

266
00:14:20,670 --> 00:14:22,400
that I had to put on a brave face.

267
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,870
You don't know.

268
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,750
For so many times,

269
00:14:35,260 --> 00:14:36,320
when I look at you,

270
00:14:37,270 --> 00:14:38,930
it's like looking in a mirror.

271
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:42,470
It's like looking at another me.

272
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:51,550
Ye Xian.

273
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:55,840
To me,

274
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:58,010
you are extremely special.

275
00:15:15,460 --> 00:15:16,420
But...

276
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:20,240
I cannot love you.

277
00:15:22,270 --> 00:15:24,150
Because we are both that kind of people

278
00:15:24,150 --> 00:15:25,840
who are panicked inside,

279
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,080
but on the outside,

280
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,410
are stubborn and tough.

281
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:30,120
We like to act tough

282
00:15:30,670 --> 00:15:32,270
and say things we don't mean.

283
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,690
We clearly want to be cared for,

284
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,530
but dare not say it out loud.

285
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:40,670
