00:34:31,370 --> 00:34:35,179
Conferred by the Great Yan]

557
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:50,590
Bow to Heaven and Earth!

558
00:34:54,190 --> 00:34:55,199
[Chen Yanzhang,
Second Master of the Chen family]

559
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,360
Bow to parents!

560
00:35:21,510 --> 00:35:23,960
Husband and wife bow to each other!

561
00:35:36,820 --> 00:35:38,830
An imperial edict has arrived!

562
00:35:41,700 --> 00:35:44,690
[Imperial Edict]

563
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:43,920
By the grace of Heaven, the Emperor

564
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:44,860
decrees:

565
00:35:45,920 --> 00:35:47,760
I have inherited the great mandate

566
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:49,360
to rule over all directions.

567
00:35:49,480 --> 00:35:51,630
I promote education to rectify
moral relations

568
00:35:51,630 --> 00:35:54,230
and value titles to distinguish
good and evil.

569
00:35:54,230 --> 00:35:56,230
As for the rules of the inner chambers,

570
00:35:56,230 --> 00:35:57,800
they are crucial to morals.

571
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:59,800
A woman's honor comes from her husband.

572
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:01,940
This is in line with the state's
system.

573
00:36:01,940 --> 00:36:03,440
Chen Yanyun,
Grand Secretary of the Eastern Cabinet

574
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:04,630
and Left Vice Minister of Revenue,

575
00:36:04,630 --> 00:36:06,920
now has a wife, Gu.

576
00:36:06,620 --> 00:36:09,760
[Imperial Edict]

577
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:08,550
Gu has made contributions to the people.

578
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:10,360
With her virtuous and gentle nature,

579
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:13,110
she is now conferred of
the second-rank titled lady.

580
00:36:13,110 --> 00:36:15,450
Gu shall abide by this.

581
00:36:15,510 --> 00:36:17,550
May you respectfully accept
this grand decree

582
00:36:17,550 --> 00:36:19,550
and forever establish a virtuous model.

583
00:36:19,550 --> 00:36:21,210
Respect this!

584
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:25,880
Long live His Majesty!

585
00:36:34,520 --> 00:36:36,720
Madam Chen, please receive the decree.

586
00:36:37,110 --> 00:36:37,960
I

587
00:36:38,340 --> 00:36:40,670
thank His Majesty for his profound grace!

588
00:36:56,710 --> 00:36:57,550
Usually,

589
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,070
only when an official makes a contribution

590
00:36:59,070 --> 00:37:01,070
does his wife get an imperial title.

591
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:03,480
Yet His Majesty decreed on the day
of Jiuheng's wedding

592
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:05,140
to grant Gu an imperial title.

593
00:37:06,030 --> 00:37:08,360
This is truly unprecedented in Great Yan.

594
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:10,830
Jiuheng is a diligent official.

595
00:37:11,030 --> 00:37:12,960
His Majesty naturally trusts him.

596
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:15,550
As for Gu,

597
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:18,600
I only hope she is worthy of it.

598
00:37:29,070 --> 00:37:30,880
That coronet is so heavy.

599
00:37:31,670 --> 00:37:33,070
My neck is about to break.

600
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:34,360
Thank goodness

601
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:35,760
you were here to help me take it off

602
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:36,850
and redo my hair.

603
00:37:37,110 --> 00:37:38,770
So much more comfortable now.

604
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,480
My Lady,

605
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:41,710
you were so glorious today.

606
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,440
I don't know why,

607
00:37:48,550 --> 00:37:50,550
but I've been feeling very anxious.

608
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:53,680
Maybe you're just nervous about
getting married.

609
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:54,440
No.

610
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:57,480
Earlier when we were on the street,

611
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:58,920
and ran into a funeral procession,

612
00:37:58,920 --> 00:37:59,980
did you see clearly

613
00:38:00,070 --> 00:38:01,150
whose family it was?

614
00:38:01,150 --> 00:38:02,620
I felt it was bad luck,

615
00:38:02,710 --> 00:38:03,970
so I didn't look at all.

616
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:05,860
I just saw a patch of white.

617
00:38:08,590 --> 00:38:09,920
I think

618
00:38:10,370 --> 00:38:12,000
I heard Ye Xian's voice.

619
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:15,480
I really didn't see him.

620
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,320
My Lady,

621
00:38:19,510 --> 00:38:21,040
you might be overthinking.

622
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,000
Last night,

623
00:38:22,070 --> 00:38:22,800
didn't His Lordship

624
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:23,800
come to see you?

625
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:26,960
Madam!

626
00:38:33,030 --> 00:38:34,630
Third Master was worried
you might be hungry,

627
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:37,430
so he ordered us to bring
the banquet food up first.

628
00:38:39,030 --> 00:38:40,150
Come on.

629
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:41,000
Thank you all

630
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,670
for coming in person to congratulate me.

631
00:38:42,670 --> 00:38:43,530
I

632
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:44,880
would like to toast you all!

633
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:46,110
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations!

634
00:38:46,110 --> 00:38:47,320
Congratulations!

635
00:38:49,510 --> 00:38:50,360
Cheers.

636
00:38:52,110 --> 00:38:53,030
Congratulations.

637
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:53,800
Congratulations.

638
00:38:53,800 --> 00:38:55,880
Congratulations, Old Madam.

639
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,930
My Lady, this is delicious.

640
00:39:24,190 --> 00:39:26,000
Eat more if you like it.

641
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:31,390
I think

642
00:39:31,630 --> 00:39:32,430
you are right.

643
00:39:33,110 --> 00:39:35,230
Ye Xian just came to see me last night,

644
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:37,920
so nothing bad should have happened.

645
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:38,840
My Lady, I feel

646
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:40,760
you shouldn't worry about Young Lord Ye.

647
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:42,820
You should worry about Third Master.

648
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:44,230
Worry about Third Master?

649
00:39:44,230 --> 00:39:44,920
Why?

650
00:39:45,510 --> 00:39:46,440
Last night,

651
00:39:46,670 --> 00:39:47,870
there was such a fuss.

652
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:50,710
Aren't you afraid Third Master
will get angry?

653
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:53,070
He might be

654
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:55,700
a bit upset, I suppose.

655
00:39:56,030 --> 00:39:57,800
But it wasn't directed at me.

656
00:39:58,590 --> 00:40:00,440
You're already eating the feast
he sent over,

657
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:02,300
and you still worry he'd be petty?

658
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:04,760
True.

659
00:40:06,190 --> 00:40:07,990
I heard the servants say earlier

660
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:09,930
that Third Master is very caring.

661
00:40:11,070 --> 00:40:12,320
He made such a big show

662
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:13,780
of sending this food over.

663
00:40:14,030 --> 00:40:15,320
It's it because he was worried

664
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:18,180
that the people in the mansion would
look down on me?

665
00:40:20,150 --> 00:40:21,120
Eat slowly.

666
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:22,440
After you finish,

667
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:23,940
go to the front hall.

668
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,360
There are many people today.

669
00:40:25,360 --> 00:40:26,590
Don't let him drink too much,

670
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:28,400
and send him some hangover soup as well.

671
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:28,920
Okay.

672
00:40:53,550 --> 00:40:54,610
Congratulations.

673
00:40:55,070 --> 00:40:56,130
Thank you, Mentor.

674
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:00,510
Please.

675
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:02,070
Come on.

676
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:06,400
Marquis Changxing has passed away.

677
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:07,550
You must have heard.

678
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:10,880
Yes.

679
00:41:13,550 --> 00:41:15,230
His Majesty intends

680
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:18,060
for Ye Xian to inherit the title.

681
00:41:18,800 --> 00:41:20,400
That cannot happen, Mentor.

682
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,130
We finally

683
00:41:26,160 --> 00:41:27,590
waited for Marquis Changxing to die.

684
00:41:27,590 --> 00:41:30,230
How could we let Ye Xian
inherit the title?

685
00:41:34,110 --> 00:41:35,990
I heard that last night

686
00:41:36,150 --> 00:41:37,950
he caused trouble for you again.

687
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:41,270
Just the struggle of a cornered beast.

688
00:41:41,270 --> 00:41:42,870
It's nothing to worry about.

689
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,730
Please, please.

690
00:41:51,310 --> 00:41:52,910
Come on, have another glass.

691
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:54,480
This...

692
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:58,250
Jiuheng, you've been resting at home
for a long time, right?

693
00:41:58,360 --> 00:42:01,220
Go back to Hall of Literary Profundity
in a few days.

694
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:02,670
Great.

695
00:42:02,670 --> 00:42:03,600
Quick, Jiuheng!

696
00:42:07,550 --> 00:42:08,610
Thank you, Mentor.

697
00:42:09,230 --> 00:42:10,680
Xuanweng's high regard for Jiuheng

698
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:12,280
is truly unquestionable.

699
00:42:16,010 --> 00:42:16,530
Drink!

700
00:42:16,670 --> 00:42:17,620
Drink, drink.

701
00:42:17,990 --> 00:42:18,910
Drink, drink.

702
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:24,840
Mentor, your kindness to me

703
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:26,280
is like a second chance at life.

704
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:28,050
It makes me deeply ashamed.

705
00:42:28,510 --> 00:42:30,090
We are teacher and student.

706
00:42:30,320 --> 00:42:31,230
No need for formalities.

707
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:31,690
Come on.

708
00:42:32,490 --> 00:42:32,950
Come on.

709
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:33,710
Let's drink.

710
00:42:33,710 --> 00:42:34,590
Come on, drink.

711
00:42:34,610 --> 00:42:35,590
Please.

712
00:42:37,110 --> 00:42:37,920
Please.

713
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:38,480
Come on.

714
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:40,760
Good wine.

715
00:42:41,360 --> 00:42:42,950
Drink more tonight.

716
00:42:45,190 --> 00:42:46,480
Xuruo, you look like

717
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:49,080
you have something on your mind.

718
00:42:50,230 --> 00:42:50,670
No.

719
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:52,960
I...

720
00:42:54,630 --> 00:42:55,280
I'm happy.

721
00:42:56,630 --> 00:42:57,280
Happy?

722
00:42:58,110 --> 00:43:00,310
What kind of happiness looks like that?

723
00:43:14,070 --> 00:43:14,590
Xuruo!

724
00:43:16,670 --> 00:43:17,760
Let him be!

725
00:43:17,790 --> 00:43:18,400
Come on,

726
00:43:18,400 --> 00:43:18,960
let's keep drinking.

727
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:19,760
Let's drink up.

728
00:43:19,760 --> 00:43:20,620
Come on, drink.

729
00:43:30,630 --> 00:43:31,590
Gu Jinzhao.

730
00:43:46,380 --> 00:43:49,800
[A Splendid Match]
